==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exultant
<hw>Ex*ult"ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>exsultans</ets>, <ets>exsultantis</ets>, p. pr. of
<ets>exsultare</ets>. See <er>Exult</er>.]</ety> <def>Inclined to exult;
characterized by, or expressing, exultation; rejoicing
triumphantly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Break away, <qex>exultant</qex>, from every defilement.</q>
<rj><qau>I. Tay;or.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exultation</ent>⟦br⟧
